## Description {#details}

Iterator class that can traverse the differentially encoded values in DiffLists.

Don&#39;t use this class directly, use one of the adaptors below.

Definition at line 198 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/mc/mcregisterinfo-h">MCRegisterInfo.h</a>.
